h1. Yoolink Typo Sidebar

This script is a plugin for Typo blog (http://typosphere.org).
With this plugin you can display your last link bookmark by
yoolink (http://yoolink.fr).

h2. Installation

download this plugin and copy it in your directory /vendor/plugin/

h2. Configuration

In plugin part in typo admin, the configuration of this plugin are :

 * login : Your login in yoolink
 * items limit : the number of items see in sidebar
 * groups link by days : all bookmark are group by day
 * Allow links in description : by default all link in description of bookmark
   are desable. but you can activate
